@WHO ? Dude the reason why people hate this is simply cause they care for the girl. It isn't just rape that pisses them off. At least it isn't for me. It's whatever I see a tragedy of any kind. I personally hate tragedies. Whether it's something as lttle as hentai to masterpieces like Romeo and Juliet. I like to emotionally investe into characters. It's how I'm able to understand their thoughts, feelings, and goals. Saying that we shouldn't care cause it's fiction is like saying we shouldn't feel joy when Naruto's hard work has been acknowledged, anger when Frieza kills Krillin, saddness when Kuro-Sensei's students kill him. It's what art is supposed to do and it's what it's trying captivate. So yes some people are enraged by this awful genre and there's nothing wrong with that. Nor is there defending it. It's your fetish. Doesn't mean we have to accept that. We know fully well it'll continue, all that we want is for people to agree it's horrible and disgusting. And maybe less rape.
